casebody.data:
Pedro MORAN-ALVARDO, Plaintiff,
v.
NEVADA COURT REALTY, LLC, EZ Donuts, t/a/ Dunkin' Donuts, Defendants,
and
Nevada Court Realty, LLC, Defendant/Third-Party Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
EZ Donuts, Inc. and M & M, Landscaping, Third-Party Defendants,
and
Travelers Insurance Company, Third-Party Defendant-Respondent. C-1008 September Term 2017
081134 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 6, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004164-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
